    <article id="main-content" class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="How to Redeem Your Star Atlas How to Redeem Your Star Atlas UE5 Game Key Game Key" class="article-title">
          How to Redeem Your Star Atlas How to Redeem Your Star Atlas UE5 Game Key Game Key
          
        </h1>

        <div class="article-author">
          
          <div class="article-meta">
            

            <div class="meta-group">
              
                <span class="meta-data"><time datetime="2025-12-08T21:06:12Z" title="2025-12-08T21:06:12Z" data-datetime="relative">December 08, 2025 21:06</time></span>
                <span class="meta-data">Updated</span>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        
          <div class="article-subscribe"><div data-helper="subscribe" data-json="{&quot;item&quot;:&quot;article&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/hc/en-us/articles/47210147406483-How-to-Redeem-Your-Star-Atlas-How-to-Redeem-Your-Star-Atlas-UE5-Game-Key-Game-Key/subscription.json&quot;,&quot;follow_label&quot;:&quot;Follow&quot;,&quot;unfollow_label&quot;:&quot;Unfollow&quot;,&quot;following_label&quot;:&quot;Following&quot;,&quot;can_subscribe&quot;:true,&quot;is_subscribed&quot;:false}"></div></div>
        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><h3 id="h_01KBZWJ2X80KGPRG7RSA9HGHPY">Redeem via Epic Games Launcher</h3><ol data-start="398" data-end="785">
<li data-start="398" data-end="435" data-list-item-id="ee82f70906165c091871ca85621abe4b4"><p data-start="401" data-end="435"><strong data-start="401" data-end="409">Open</strong> the Epic Games Launcher</p></li>
<li data-start="436" data-end="478" data-list-item-id="e2dd9db5014ce7dee5c7fdbe5547db5f0"><p data-start="439" data-end="478"><strong data-start="439" data-end="449">Log in</strong> to your Epic Games account</p></li>
<li data-start="479" data-end="533" data-list-item-id="e85d793042104908d5b1a68ab30a64084"><p data-start="482" data-end="533">Click your <strong data-start="493" data-end="505">username</strong> in the upper-right corner</p></li>
<li data-start="534" data-end="561" data-list-item-id="ee40259a673f196681b1b79228e8ebdc4"><p data-start="537" data-end="561">Select <strong data-start="544" data-end="559">Redeem Code</strong></p></li>
<li data-start="562" data-end="611" data-list-item-id="e3bf745cb5b8a6e3e1599f6fcb2468386"><p data-start="565" data-end="611"><strong data-start="565" data-end="588">Enter your game key</strong> and click <strong data-start="599" data-end="609">Redeem</strong></p></li>
<li data-start="612" data-end="649" data-list-item-id="e6cd8029fcc4748609b6ec69266384493"><p data-start="615" data-end="649">You should see a success message</p></li>
<li data-start="650" data-end="712" data-list-item-id="eae5ecd4fa58d6af58f1a789fbb10a5e2"><p data-start="653" data-end="712">Click <strong data-start="659" data-end="675">Back to Home</strong> to return to the launcher homepage</p></li>
<li data-start="713" data-end="785" data-list-item-id="e440e9b0f30c13d37ca1951e1c4f7f059"><p data-start="716" data-end="785">Go to your <strong data-start="727" data-end="738">Library,</strong> Star Atlas should be there, ready to install</p></li>
</ol><h3 id="h_01KBZWJ2X84FCQDW6AWHX3XF1Q">&nbsp;</h3><h3 id="h_01KBZWJH5G0RG4FWTRERT8FJ5K">Redeem via Epic Games Store Website</h3><ol data-start="835" data-end="1210">
<li data-start="835" data-end="937" data-list-item-id="ea0c89604fb993caa2c6b44fa57e418ac"><p data-start="838" data-end="937">Open your browser and go to&nbsp; <a href="https://www.epicgames.com/store" data-start="869" data-end="935" target="_new" rel="noopener">https://www.epicgames.com/store</a></p></li>
<li data-start="938" data-end="976" data-list-item-id="ee2364554c91c358fef2e5c0c560124f3"><p data-start="941" data-end="976">Log in to your Epic Games account</p></li>
<li data-start="977" data-end="1038" data-list-item-id="eb53646ecc7a398873a0f34a897786738"><p data-start="980" data-end="1038">Hover over your <strong data-start="996" data-end="1012">profile name</strong> in the top-right corner</p></li>
<li data-start="1039" data-end="1065" data-list-item-id="eb37bb529345d9f37d094567043b9c5d2"><p data-start="1042" data-end="1065">Click <strong data-start="1048" data-end="1063">Redeem Code</strong></p></li>
<li data-start="1066" data-end="1111" data-list-item-id="ee3d94f03a2ddf89ec9f4f90f59ab81f1"><p data-start="1069" data-end="1111">Enter your game key and click <strong data-start="1099" data-end="1109">Redeem</strong></p></li>
<li data-start="1112" data-end="1161" data-list-item-id="e3210deb2330cfc3049a73b71506ecca4"><p data-start="1115" data-end="1161">Once confirmed, open the Epic Games Launcher</p></li>
<li data-start="1162" data-end="1210" data-list-item-id="e2055cd68db7af6e4f2e1218b25f22efe"><p data-start="1165" data-end="1210">Your game will now appear in your <strong data-start="1199" data-end="1210">Library</strong></p></li>
</ol></div>

          

          
        </div>
      </section>

